  FREQUENTLY ASKED QUESTIONS

  * Is my financial data stored on any server?
  -> No. All your data stays on your device. Unchained Money does not collect, transmit, or store any personal or financial information externally.

  * How is my debt-free date calculated?
  -> The app uses the avalanche method — prioritising loans with the highest interest rates first — along with your income, expenses, and savings to project
  a realistic debt-free timeline.

  * Can I update my financial details after onboarding?
  -> Yes. Go to the Profile tab and tap "Update Financial Data" to edit your income, expenses, loans, or assets at any time.

  * How do I delete all my data?
  -> Go to Profile → Clear All Data. This permanently removes everything from your device.

  * The app shows a deficit warning. What does that mean?
  -> Your monthly expenses and EMIs exceed your income. The app will suggest ways to address this, such as reducing expenses or increasing income.

  ABOUT THE APP
  Unchained Money is a personal finance tool that helps you visualise your path to becoming debt-free. It generates a personalised roadmap based on your
  financial situation — no sign-up, no server, no tracking.
